2.  We will remove the `generator` attribute from the `@GeneratedValue` annotation, as it is no longer needed.
3.  We will update the `sequenceName` attribute in the `@SequenceGenerator` annotation to match the sequence name required by Hibernate (i.e., `<entity name>_seq`).
4.  We will update the `allocationSize` attribute in the `@SequenceGenerator` annotation to match the allocation size required by Hibernate (i.e., 1).

